name: Cryptocurrency Historical Prices
content:
Description: Data on the prices of Bitcoin, Ethereum, and Dogecoin from 2013-2021.

Source: [Kaggle](https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/sudalairajkumar/cryptocurrencypricehistory)

Columns:

* Name (string): Name of the cryptocurrency
* Symbol (string): Symbol for the cryptocurrency
* Year (numerical): The year of the date (2013-2021)
* Month (numerical): The month of the date (1-12)
* Day (numerical): The day of the date (1-31)
* Date (string): the date in MM/DD/YYYY format
* Price(numerical): the price of the cryptocurrency at the time of the market closing that day
